[Output structure] ### `default` format

```json
{
  "indicator": {
    "title": "RSI",
    "overlay": false
  },
  "plots": {
    "RSI": {
      "title": "RSI",
      "options": { "color": "#7E57C2" },
      "data": [
        { "time": 1704067200000, "value": 58.23 },
        { "time": 1704070800000, "value": 61.45 }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

### `full` format

Adds `result` (raw return values per bar) and `marketData` (OHLCV candles) to the default output.
